                <p class="hero-sub">Kuda is a full-service digital agency specializing in scalable web applications, stunning UI/UX design, and growth-driven marketing strategies.</p>
                <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                    <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-green">Start a Project <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ms-2"></i></a>
                    <a href="#services" class="btn btn-ghost">See Our Work</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-5">
                <div class="row g-3">
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <div class="hero-card">
                            <div class="hero-card-num">150+</div>
